item.title: Return of the Meme: 1538 (Emotional Processing)
item.description:
Let's get this bread. Got fired yesterday afternoon. Built this dump as a coping mechanism afterwards.
Also stopped by the Sedona Wetlands Preserve on my way home from being fired, and saw my first ever Red-breasted Merganser.
This dump is darker than i feel this morning, after a night of processing, but... Yes. I am a failure at once again serving the interests of the ruling class.
I choked at the test of remembering the Six Forbes Standards connected to the Eight Principles and the 24 Rules of behavior to the 36 Tenants of Masking your Neurodivergence. Failed. Because what the goddamn fuck. I studied wrote everything like thirty times to memorize it and just... brain no work. And the test is a 2 times and you're out.
On the bright side I won't be stress vomiting in the mornings about work now.
Course, now I have entirely different reasons to stress-vomit in the morning now.
I'm not going to miss the nightmares about that damned booking system, either. I swear thing thing was built purposely ass-backwards to make things as difficult as possible.
This actually happened as I took the test.
Ugh. I feel like such a failure, even though i HATED this job with a passion. Combined with relief and indifference. And Hunger. I decided last night not to eat so I could thereby punish myself and suffer? Because that made so much sense in the moment. Brains are ridiculous.
But it really does seem like I'm good at nothing that actually makes money. And my brain feels like this meme sometimes.
The past sucked ROYAL ass in so many ways, but at least there would have been a place for a weirdo like myself.
I have no idea what i'm going to do, but I know death is not a real option, even if the suicide memes are lit.
I am a ginkgo. I was designed for a world that no longer exists, and i survive only by stubbornness and the help of others.
I mean, this was me last night so it wasnt exactly pleasant trying to sleep.
Woke up after a night of absolute shitty sleep, but hey, now I won't need 5 cups of coffee to be human!
Yeah. This is also me, I guess when I wear my Scythian hat, hahahah.
It is what it is.
I had a thought yesterday after it all went down about throwing on my bronze age garb and going up to the mountain today and taking *all of the meds* with a bottle of my Bronze-age mead, but it would have sucked to be stuck up there when I'd just wake up with the hangover from hell, with a now ruined liver, and no gas to come home, just to give the ruling elites what they want? Eh. No. Pippin would have been pretty cross about it too.
Mood.
Mood.
I was also having a crumb of hope for the first time that things would be okay, so my irrational brain is saying "This is why you shouldn't feel hope! The universe and God hates you! You aren't supposed to be happy!" That's probably bullshit on my brain's part.
Luckily i have a 3-D printed model of my brain now that i can beat up and throw against the wall, and ground, instead of punching myself in the head like I used to do as a coping mechanism ? I found yesterday that it actually helped to do that, and didn't leave me with a headache afterwards, and actually left me happier than sadder when I threw it against the wall a few times. I'm not sure my former therapist would say that would count as progress, but it's. It's something.
Okay. So what next. Maybe my application for the AZ state insurance will actually be accepted. If it is, definitely changing meds. I'm honestly suprised i'm holding up as well as I am now, honestly, and not continuing to spiral downward: I'm just spiraling horizontally. Honestly, not sure how else to describe how i'm feeling other than "spiraling horizontally."
Mood.
I used to know when I was younger what I wanted to be and what I wanted from life. The only thing that vision and me now have in common is an avian companion.
Yeahhhhh, this is a good approach.
Mood.
Brain. Staaahp.
Accurate.
Is it that i'm so used to all this shit that my brain isn't spiraling down anymore because this is just... normal now?
Mood.
I tried to be something I wasn't for these people. It is what it is.
Hahahahah this is funny only if you are a gnostic really.
Also knowing that there are people who actually would miss me, and not just because of the memes. And there's beauty in the world I still want to see.
Yeaaah.
I swear, as of this morning, i'm good. I used this dump to process the mood. I helldived, went to bed. Its not the end. I dont know what it is, but it's not the end. I should scrounge up breakfast, but bed is so comfortable and Pippin is contentedly beak grinding on my head so he's also comfy.
If my brain wants me to die, it will have to do it itself. I will not carry out it's dirty work.
I won't lie, if i was by the sea, keeping myself alive would be A LOT HARDER right now, if only because the inevitable sarcastic dark comment someone would make about me even failing at being a successful Sea Person. (Bronze Age history joke)
So ill have another fucking gap jn my resume, I guess. I wish I had more money to play outside right now, but it is what it is.
Let's do this. Time to crawl out of another hole. At this point I've probably worn an easy fucking path out of it.
Things will get better. Somehow.
There is, but there's no name for it.
I hope you all have an okay day today.
Pippin tax (shown eating Turkey) Today's message from Pippin: "I love you too." ______ 1) Are you on the run to a safe place and passing through Arizona on your way to safer grounds? My apartment is open to you to crash at, and it is a safe space. Pippin and I will make you a meal and gladly share tea, wine, or mead with you. 2) Hey! Take your meds with a full glass of water, please. Do it for Pippin, or Space Mom, or better yet, do it for yourself. 3) Ĝefeloað wē. We will carry on. 4) all funds from the sales of items at these two links will be sent to support charities aiding to fight for Trans rights in the US (not just T-shirts!) https://www.teepublic.com/t-shirt/74812801-all-conures-are-anarchists https://www.teepublic.com/t-shirt/74811778-whiptail-pride 5) Since multiple people have requested this over the last two weeks or so, my ko-fi is: https://ko-fi.com/codyandpippin 6) There is now a discord server. https://discord.gg/qadbfR9A

item.title: So I got a call at 2:00am this morning…
item.description:
(Reposting because Bestie’s name was shown on one of the pictures) Bestie and a friend went out to the bar last night, and I got a call at 2:00am that she had been rushed to the ER by ambulance. She all of a sudden couldn’t walk or talk, and was falling over. Before they left, her friend took a video of her drink. Look at all the white stuff floating around
I rushed to the ER with a phone charger and some food, and hung out for a while. All the bloodwork came back negative for drugs. The doc assumes it was some kind of sedative or anti-psychotic that wouldn’t show up on the tests
Bestie got a signed document for me and her friend to show work to call off because we “helped with the emergency.” I didn’t use it, but it was nice of her to offer
She is all good now. Slept all day, just called me to check in, is gonna take a bath and go back to bed. She’s just really tired, no other lingering effects. Wants to come see the kittens first thing tomorrow. Which tells me she really is feeling better. Watch your drinks, people.
